HOW TO APPLY THIS LICENSE TO YOUR DEPLOYMENT
--------------------------------------------

If you deploy the SGU Logistics & Telemetry Dashboard, include the
following notice in a visible location within the dashboard interface:

    Powered by SGU Logistics & Telemetry Dashboard
    Copyright (c) 2025–2026 moonr5
    Licensed under the SGU Logistics Source Available License v1.0

For the Arduino firmware (GPS_device.ino, obd2_scanner.ino), include
this notice at the top of each source file:

    /*
     * SGU Logistics & Telemetry — Embedded Firmware
     * Copyright (c) 2025–2026 moonr5
     * Licensed under the SGU Logistics Source Available License v1.0
     * See LICENSE file in the project root for full terms.
     */


